Type: Package
Package: mtsdesc
Title: Plots and Tables for Describing Multivariate Time Series
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "SemiÃ£o", , "ricardo.semiao@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Describe multivariate time series with tables and ggplots.
    mtsdesc provides commonly needed utilities when working with a set of
    time series, i.e. multi-panel plots and multi-column summary- and
    testing-tables. The package also has methods to work with residuals of
    fitter values of multivariate time series models.
